@startuml
!include _style.puml
title AS-IS 06 — UML 시퀀스: 두 Atlas의 오래된 상태 선택

actor User
participant "Parent v17 flush" as Parent
participant "studyAtlas iframe" as Study
participant "globalAtlas iframe" as Global
database "parent localStorage" as LS
participant "Normalized Sync" as Sync
database "Supabase" as Server

note over Study
  state.title = "INITIAL"
end note
note over Global
  state.title = "LATEST_GLOBAL"
end note
note over LS
  title = "LATEST_GLOBAL"
end note

User -> Parent : 지금 저장
Parent -> Parent : v17ActiveAtlasFrames()\n[studyAtlas, globalAtlas]
Parent -> Study : ipe-atlas-export-request
Study --> Parent : response(state="INITIAL")
Parent -> Parent : first valid response에서 break

note right of Parent
  globalAtlas에는 요청하지 않거나
  응답을 비교하지 않는다. [S]
end note

Parent -> LS : Atlas = "INITIAL"
Parent --> Sync : payload.atlas = "INITIAL"
Sync -> Server : commit stale snapshot
Server --> Sync : revision saved
Sync -> LS : verified stale snapshot

note over LS,Server
  결과: 최신 global 상태와 기존 localStorage가
  오래된 study 상태로 역행한다. [R]
end note

caption 결함 1 — 복사본에 공통 revision/freshness가 없어 배열 순서가 사실상 권위가 된다.
@enduml
